Hi again! I\'ve been looking forward to 0.16, so i was planning to make a few planes in preparation for the update.

Firstly, we have my rocket plane:

It\'s capable of flying to 26,000m and a distance of 1,800,000m. I\'m working on a longer range version capable of travelling around kerbin, or to 3,500,000m.

it uses the Damned Aerospace mod.

MORE SOON!
I\'ll be working on the Rocket/Plane today because of the poll. Please comment if you\'d like to send a request!
